article_title: Watch: Brian Williams Raps Snoop Dogg's 'Who Am I?'
article_text:
SIGN UP FOR OUR NEWSLETTER

On Monday’s broadcast of NBC’s “The Tonight Show,” Jimmy Fallon and his crew commemorated the show’s return to Los Angeles for the first time since Fallon took over with a cut of “NBC Nightly News” anchor Brian Williams “rapping” Snoop Dogg’s 1993 hit “Who Am I?”
